    "commit_subject": "Add Mira Core Phase 17 storage retention validation package",
    "baseline_status": "phase_17_storage_retention_green",
    "baseline_boundary": "Phase 17 defines storage/deletion/export/retention validation only. No real Mira Core server database, schema migration, audit-log runtime, network path, queue, local execution, send, deploy, trade, memory/profile commit, export, deletion, restore, or raw-content storage exists at this baseline."
  },
